## 📄 Project Files

### `pyproject.toml` (Dependencies & Metadata)
```toml
[project]
name = "bookstore-api"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "FastAPI + Tortoise ORM Bookstore API"
requires-python = ">=3.11"
dependencies = [
    "fastapi>=0.110.0",
    "uvicorn[standard]>=0.29.0",
    "tortoise-orm[asyncpg]>=0.20.0",
    "aerich>=0.8.0",
